   "source": [
    "## 8. Key Business Insights\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Champions drive outsized revenue.** 18.6% of customers generate 31.9% of all \n",
    "   revenue. Protecting this group — loyalty rewards, early product drops, personal \n",
    "   thank-you emails — is the highest-ROI action.\n",
    "\n",
    "2. **At Risk is the highest-urgency segment.** 7,974 customers who bought multiple \n",
    "   times haven't returned in 263 days on average. A targeted re-engagement campaign \n",
    "   here is the most recoverable revenue in the business right now.\n",
    "\n",
    "3. **Most customers only order once.** Median frequency = 1. This is a retention \n",
    "   problem, not an acquisition problem. A post-purchase email flow could shift \n",
    "   this meaningfully over time.\n",
    "\n",
    "4. **Frequency drives spend more than recency.** The heatmap shows F=5 customers \n",
    "   spend 3x more than any other group regardless of recency. Getting customers \n",
    "   to a second and third order is the single biggest lever for revenue growth."
   ]
  },
